<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1940-05-09T11:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1940-05-09T11:00:00-05:00" n="925" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d925">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">390D.11/196: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Turkey</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Ankara</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-05-09T18:00:00+02:00">May 9,
                                        1940—6 p.m.</date>
                                    <lb/> [Received May 9—4:14 p.m.]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>50. Department’s 26, April 26, 4 p.m. Being apprehensive of a
                                deadlock in our negotiations I discussed the matter yesterday with
                                the Foreign Minister.<note n="65" xml:id="d925fn65">Sükrü
                                    Saracoglu</note> He said that he himself was not yet fully
                                convinced that our proposals were altogether satisfactory. He
                                promised, however, to interest himself personally in trying to work
                                out a satisfactory arrangement.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">MacMurray</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>